<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
  <metadata>
    <id>calibre</id>
    <title>Calibre</title>
    <version>0.9.30</version>
    <authors>Kovid Goyal</authors>
    <owners>Gary Ewan Park</owners>
    <summary>calibre is the one stop solution to all your e-book needs.</summary>
    <description>calibre is a free and open source e-book library management application developed by users of e-books for users of e-books.</description>
    <projectUrl>http://calibre-ebook.com/</projectUrl>
    <tags>ebook library management</tags>
    <copyright>Kovid Goyal</copyright>
    <licenseUrl>http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html</licenseUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <iconUrl>https://github.com/gep13/ChocolateyPackages/raw/master/calibre/calibre.ico</iconUrl>
    <releaseNotes>
    - New: Kobo driver: Add support for showing 'Archived' books on the device. Also up the supported firmware version to 2.5.3.
    - New: Driver for Blackberry 9790
	- New: Add a tweak to turn off the highlighting of the book count when using a virtual library (Preferences - Tweaks)
	- New: Add a button to clear the viewer search history in the viewer Preferences, under Miscellaneous
	- New: Add keyboard shortcuts to clear the virtual Library and the additional restriction (Ctrl+Esc and Alt+Esc). Also use Shift+Esc to bring keyboard focus back tot he book list. Can be changed under Preferences - Keyboard
	- New: Docx metadata: Read the language of the file, if present
    - Fixed: Kobo driver: Fix unable to read SD card on OS X/Linux
    - Fixed: Content server: Fix unable to download ORIGINAL_* formats
    - Fixed: Fix regression that broke searching for terms containing a quote mark
    - Fixed: Fix regression that broke conversion of txt files when no input encoding is specified
	- Fixed: When changing to a virtual library, refresh the Book Details panel.
	- Fixed: Fix regression that caused searching for user categories to break.
	- Fixed: Fix error when downloading only covers and reviewing downloaded metadata.
	- Fixed: MOBI metadata: Strip XML unsafe unicode codepoints when reading metadata from MOBI files.
	- Fixed: Txt Input: Use the gbk encoding for txt files with detected encoding of gb2312.
	- Fixed: When pressing Ctrl+Home/End preserve the horizontal scroll position in the book list
    - Improved News Source: NSFW
    - Improved News Source: Go Comics
	- Improved News Source: Various Polish news sources
	- Improved News Source: The Sun
    </releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
</package>
